com.itko.lisa.remote

Class AgentInfo2

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.itko.lisa.remote.AgentInfo2
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IAgentInfo, java.io.Serializable

    public class AgentInfo2
extends java.lang.Object
implements IAgentInfo
    This class encapsulates information about an agent that is then made public to all interested parties so they can later subscribe to this agent events or invoke APIs on it.
    See Also:
    IAgentInfo, Serialized Form
